    "created_at": "2014-05-17T00:46:09Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-05-17T00:46:09Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Thinking about it some more, I don't like the 'prefix' solution - the per-user kernel directory does not end with `share/ipython/kernels`, so you can't put a default value for the user installation location. It also doesn't work on Windows, where the system directory doesn't end in `share/ipython/kernels`.\n\nI think we should merge this as is, and work out what to do about /usr/local/share at some later point.\n"
  },
