    "updated_at": "2014-06-03T23:29:37Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "After discussion with @minrk , I have made this look in both `/usr/share/ipython/kernels` and `/usr/local/share/ipython/kernels`, and provided an installation mechanism only for `/usr/local/...`. Packagers will have to copy/move the kernel spec directory to `/usr/...` using standard commands - this doesn't seem like a big problem.\n\nTravis gives 9e702fi the [green light](https://travis-ci.org/ipython/ipython/builds/26715610) (recording this because Jenkins is about to nobble the build indicator).\n\nJenkins, test on Windows, please\n"
  },
